Interface SignalGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SignalGroupImpl

    public interface SignalGroup
extends OaamBaseElementA, ModeDependentElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Signal Group'. A signal group can be used to organize signals in groups with some relationship, e.g. the same constraint

    The following features are supported:

    • Signals
